    <li><strong>Training Requirements:</strong> Minimal training required for both students and counselors; the system is designed to be self-explanatory</li>
    <li><strong>Technical Support:</strong> The platform requires minimal technical maintenance once deployed on ICP, with automatic updates and no server management overhead</li>
