<!-- PAGE 19-20: PROJECT DESCRIPTION -->
<div class="page">
  <div class="chapter-header">CHAPTER 4: PROJECT DESCRIPTION</div>
  <h3>4.1: MODULES OF PROJECT</h3>
  <p>MindCare is organized into several key modules, each serving distinct functional requirements for different user roles:</p>
  <h4>Modules for Admin:</h4>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>1. User Management:</strong> The first registered user becomes admin automatically. Admin can view all registered students and manage user accounts, roles, and access permissions.</li>
    <li><strong>2. Counselor Management:</strong> Admin can add new counselors, view existing counselors (6 pre-seeded at startup), update counselor information (name, specialization, contact), and remove inactive counselors from the system.</li>
    <li><strong>3. Assignment Oversight:</strong> Admin can view all student-counselor assignments, monitor chat activity, and reassign students to different counselors as needed.</li>
    <li><strong>4. System Configuration:</strong> Admin manages system-wide settings including counselor availability status, platform announcements, and health reminder schedules.</li>
    <li><strong>5. Analytics Dashboard:</strong> Visual overview of platform usage statistics, active counselors, and student engagement metrics.</li>
  </ul>
  <h4>Modules for Students:</h4>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>1. Registration &amp; Profile:</strong> Students can register, create their profile with name and email, and update their information at any time.</li>
    <li><strong>2. Counselor Selection:</strong> Students can browse available counselors, view their specializations, and choose their preferred counselor. The system auto-creates student profiles if needed during this process.</li>
    <li><strong>3. Real-time Chat:</strong> On-chain messaging with assigned counselor. Messages auto-refresh every 3 seconds for a seamless, real-time experience. Chat history is preserved on the blockchain.</li>
    <li><strong>4. AI Chatbot:</strong> Dedicated AI Chat page with ChatGPT-style interface. The AI recognizes 18+ mental health topics and provides immediate, empathetic responses. Crisis detection triggers 988 helpline display.</li>
    <li><strong>5. Health Reminders:</strong> Students receive automated wellness check reminders. Can view and manage upcoming health checkup schedules.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

