  <p>Testing is a critical phase in software development that ensures the application functions correctly and meets all specified requirements. MindCare underwent multiple levels of testing to verify functionality, performance, and usability.</p>
  <h3>8.1: UNIT TESTING</h3>
  <p>Unit testing involves testing individual components and functions in isolation to ensure they work correctly.</p>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Test Case ID</th><th>Component</th><th>Test Description</th><th>Expected Result</th><th>Status</th></tr>
    <tr><td>UT-01</td><td>User Registration</td><td>Register with valid name, email, password</td><td>Account created successfully</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>UT-02</td><td>User Login</td><td>Login with correct credentials</td><td>User authenticated and redirected to dashboard</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>UT-03</td><td>Counselor Creation</td><td>Admin adds new counselor</td><td>Counselor appears in list</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>UT-04</td><td>Counselor Assignment</td><td>Student selects a counselor</td><td>Assignment record created</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>UT-05</td><td>Chat Message Send</td><td>Student sends a message</td><td>Message stored on chain and displayed</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>UT-06</td><td>AI Response Generation</td><td>User types anxiety-related message</td><td>AI returns relevant anxiety response</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>UT-07</td><td>Crisis Detection</td><td>User types crisis keyword</td><td>988 helpline displayed immediately</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>UT-08</td><td>Admin Authentication</td><td>First user registered</td><td>Admin role automatically assigned</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
  </table>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 29: MORE TESTING -->
<div class="page">
  <h3>8.2: INTEGRATION TESTING</h3>
  <p>Integration testing verifies that different modules of the application work correctly together.</p>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Test Case ID</th><th>Modules Tested</th><th>Test Description</th><th>Status</th></tr>
    <tr><td>IT-01</td><td>Auth + Dashboard</td><td>Login redirects to correct dashboard based on role</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>IT-02</td><td>Counselor + Chat</td><td>After assignment, chat opens with correct counselor</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>IT-03</td><td>AI + Chat</td><td>AI responses appear inline in chat after user message</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>IT-04</td><td>Admin + Counselor</td><td>Counselors added by admin appear in student selection list</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
    <tr><td>IT-05</td><td>Reminder + Dashboard</td><td>Wellness reminders appear on student dashboard</td><td>PASS</td></tr>
  </table>
  <h3>8.3: USER ACCEPTANCE TESTING (UAT)</h3>
  <p>UAT was conducted with a group of college students to validate that the system meets their real-world needs and expectations.</p>
  <table>
    <tr><th>Feature</th><th>User Feedback</th><th>Satisfaction Rating</th></tr>
    <tr><td>Overall UI Design</td><td>Modern, clean, and visually appealing</td><td>9/10</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Ease of Registration</td><td>Simple and straightforward</td><td>9/10</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Counselor Selection</td><td>Easy to understand and use</td><td>8/10</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Chat Interface</td><td>Smooth, real-time feel is appreciated</td><td>9/10</td></tr>
    <tr><td>AI Chatbot</td><td>Helpful and responsive, covers most topics</td><td>8/10</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Crisis Support</td><td>Important and reassuring feature</td><td>10/10</td></tr>
